# --- Project data ---
# The processed, bundled §7 JSON datasets ARE committed — they are the project.
# Ignore only large RAW upstream dumps (NIST XCOM, ENSDF, ORIGEN) you process
# into those tables.
data/raw/
*.tmp
# data/build/ holds the dataset build scripts (source code, not JS build output) —
# re-include it despite the generic `build/` ignore in the Node section above.
!data/build/
!data/build/**
